collectible.name: Fauna: Turtletea
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: Escaped directly from the Beast's house, Turtletea was Beauty's best friend before leaving the mansion. It was only after she found freedom on the streets of Fauna that Turtletea discovered that she doesn't like being used for tea and that she was never efficient for that, given that the tea was cold when she arrives. Since then Turtletea has been devoted to detective activities, trying to find out who created her as the enchanted creature she is.
